data.description: Welcome to this exquisite 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom, 1-car garage solid BLOCK home nestled in the heart of St. Pete! Offering a compelling blend of style and functionality, this residence boasts a strategic advantage—say goodbye to the burdensome flood insurance costs, as this property stands resilient without requiring flood insurance yet only a half mile from gorgeous waterfront views - tropical paradise awaits.  No HOA & No CDD! Step into a home where thoughtful upgrades have already been taken care of for you.  Contemporary open floor plan and stylish transitional design elements that make this home truly captivating.  Enjoy the comfort of waterproof LVP flooring throughout, great durability for busy families and pet owners.  Beautifully updated kitchen with large island, tile back splash, stainless steel appliances, and refreshed cabinets & counters. The three generously sized bedrooms, adorned with custom-built barn doors, provide ample space for relaxation and personalization. Practical features such as washer/dryer hookups in the garage and expansive floor-to-ceiling built-in shelves add to the convenience and functionality of this home.  The AC was recently replaced in 2021, the home offers newer double pane energy efficient windows, and the orangeburg pipe, a potential source of major expenses for homes in St. Pete, has been replaced by previous owner. The exterior is equally impressive, featuring a U-shaped driveway in the front and a spacious backyard enclosed by a vinyl privacy fence. The circular driveway ensures ample parking for multiple vehicles. Boating enthusiasts will appreciate the double gate on the side, ready to accommodate the storage of an average-sized boat. With the property strategically located near three free boat ramps, accessibility is a key highlight.  Nestled in the highly coveted Greater Pinellas Point neighborhood, this home is a stone's throw away from great schools. Additionally, proximity to the skyway and boat ramp adds a touch of maritime charm—you might even catch the distant horn of a passing cruise ship from your own yard.  Situated with easy access to I-275, Downtown St. Pete (only 4miles away), the beach, boat ramps, the Skyway bridge, airports, and the renowned pink streets, this home offers an ideal location to relish the best of what St. Pete has to offer. Experience the perfect blend of comfort and convenience, with schools, Bay Vista Park, and key destinations just a short distance away. Your new home awaits in this prime St. Pete location—seamlessly combining modern living with a touch of coastal allure.
